text: Soni pandema jayaliji nkwagwila ilagasyo watiji: “E mmwe Musa! Tuwendelani kwa Ambuje wenu ligongo lya chilanga Chakwe chawatawene namwe (chanti chatutyochesye ilagasyo naga tukulupilile), chisimu naga nkututyochesya ilagasyo, chitunkulupilile kwene soni chitwaleche kwene kuwigula nomwe wanache wa Israila.”
